- [SearchProjectsAsync](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Ecosystem/ModrinthService.cs#23-56) 新增 `projectType` 参数，添加 `facets=[["project_type:{type}"]]`
- [GetTrendingAsync](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Ecosystem/ModrinthService.cs#57-62) / [GetNewestAsync](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Ecosystem/ModrinthService.cs#63-68) 同样添加 type 过滤
- 正确解析 `project_type` 到 `ModProject.Type`

